pageProduct.name: Olay Regenerist Collagen Peptide24 Serum 30ml
pageProduct.description:
Information

General Information

Olay Regenerist Collagen Peptide 24 Serum is a light, concentrated and fragrance free serum specifically formulated with tried and tested ingredients like Collagen Peptide and 99% Pure Grade Niacinamide. It is designed with a unique bioavailable technology allowing the ingredients to penetrate into the skin so you can achieve plump and bouncy skin that last all day long.

Size: 30mL

KEY FEATURES

• Instantly plumps, visibly firms and smoothens fine lines with Collagen Peptide + Niacinamide that deeply penetrates into skin.
• Hydrates skin for 24 hours long.
• Concentrated serum with light texture that smoothens and improves skin bounciness
• No added parabens, phthalates, mineral oil and synthetic dyes

Warnings

Avoid contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse eyes with water

Ingredients

Water, Dimethicone, Niacinamide, Glycerin, Panthenol, Palmitoyl Pentapeptide-4, Tremella Fuciformis Sporocarp Extract, Hydroxyacetophenone, C13-14 Isoparaffin, Laureth-4, Polysorbate 20, Laureth-7, Disodium EDTA, Polyacrylamide, Dimethicone Crosspolymer, Phenoxyethanol

Directions

Smooth evenly over cleansed face and neck before moisturizer, morning and night.
